In the spawn_amr.launch file, it is invoked also the following package: 

<node pkg="ira_laser_tools" name="laserscan_multi_merger" type="laserscan_multi_merger" output="screen">
       <param name="destination_frame" value="amr_body" />
       <param name="cloud_destination_topic" value="/merged_cloud" />
       <param name="scan_destination_topic"  value="/scan_multi" />
       <param name="laserscan_topics" value="/amr/laser_front/scan /amr/laser_back/scan" />
</node>

which can be downloaded here:

https://github.com/iralabdisco/ira_laser_tools

In the folder multi_laser, still contained in this repository, there are slightly modified version of laserscan_multi_merger.cpp and laserscan_multi_merger.cfg

